                    <h2 class="block-title">Method Data</h2>
                  <div class="content">
        <div class="field field-name-field-min-participants field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Minimum Participants:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">20</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-max-participants field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Maximum Participants:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">900 per assembly</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-min-duration field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Minimum Duration:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">1 hour, discussion unlimited</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-max-duration field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Maximum Duration:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">15 hours, discussion unlimited</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-min-cost field-type-number-integer field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Minimum Cost:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">US$50</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-max-cost field-type-number-integer field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Maximum Cost:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">US$10 000</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-participant-selection field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Participant Selection:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/method-recruitment/open-all" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Open to all</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-communication-mode field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Communication Mode:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/type-interaction-among-participants/discussion-dialogue-or-deliberation" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Discussion, Dialogue, or Deliberation</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/type-interaction-among-participants/story-telling" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Story-Telling</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-stages-other field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Stages (other):&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Face-to-face surveys during an casual event, Confirmation of acceptance similar to voting , Neighbourhood&#039;s Messenger&#039;s Network</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-public-interaction-method field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Public Interaction Method(s):&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">official website, dialogues, social networks</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-decision-methods field-type-text field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Decision Method(s):&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">Voting with ad hoc decision rule and legitimacy</div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-geographical-scope field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Geographical Scope:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/geographical-scope/international" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">International</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-typical-funding-source field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Typical Funding Source:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/entities/community-based-organization" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Community Based Organization</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/entities/individual" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Individual</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-issue-polarization field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Issue Polarization:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/polarization/3-somewhat-polarized" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">3 - Somewhat Polarized</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-issue-complexity field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Issue Technical Complexity:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/complexity/5-highly-complex" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">5 - Highly Complex</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-issue-interdependency field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Issue Interdependency	:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/interdependency/5-always-tied-other-issues" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">5 - Always Tied to Other Issues</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-influence-kind field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Kind of Influence:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/kind-influence/make-public-decisions-ie-exert-direct-authority" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Make public decisions (i.e. exert direct authority)</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/kind-influence/direct-delivery-public-services-ie-entities-other-government" typeof="skos:Concept" property="rdfs:label skos:prefLabel">Direct delivery of public services (i.e. by entities other than government)</a></div><div class="field-item even"><a href="/en/kind-influence/raise-public-awareness" typeof="skos:Concept" 